headline: These Are the 5 Worst-Performing Stocks in the Dow Jones Industrial Average With 2024 Almost Over
summary: It's been a banner year for the stock market.  Boeing (NYSE: BA) has had a rough year.  It started early as the stock price fell after the door panel on a Boeing jet flown by Alaska Airlines popped off mid-flight.
